RowFilter.Name: Null untimely
RowFilter.SQLExpression:
"N$10014" as (SELECT /*+ inline */ "COMPANY" , "COMPANY_RESPONSE" , "PRODUCT" , "DATE_RECIEVED" , "DISPUTE" , "TIMELY" , "COMPLAINT_ID"
FROM {INPUT_SOURCE} WHERE "TIMELY" is not null )

RowFilter.Name: Top Companies
RowFilter.SQLExpression:
"N$10030" as (SELECT /*+ inline */ "COMPANY" , "COMPANY_RESPONSE" , "PRODUCT" , "DATE_RECIEVED" , "DISPUTE" , "TIMELY" , "COMPLAINT_ID"
FROM {INPUT_SOURCE} WHERE "COMPANY" in ('Wells Fargo', 'JPMorgan Chase', 'Citibank', 'Bank of America', 'Ocwen', 'Nationstar Mortgage') )
RowFilter.Filter: "COMPANY" in ('Wells Fargo', 'JPMorgan Chase', 'Citibank', 'Bank of America', 'Ocwen', 'Nationstar Mortgage')
